### 🛒 Computer Vision Based Automated Billing System Demo  

This demo showcases a real-time automated billing system using YOLOv8 for product detection. The system identifies retail items through a camera 
feed and automatically calculates the total bill without requiring barcode scanning.

▶ [Watch Demo](https://youtu.be/U2QKT1qezMY)

The video demonstrates:
- Real-time object detection
- Product classification using YOLOv8
- Automatic price mapping
- Dynamic billing interface updates

The system highlights how computer vision can replace traditional checkout processes and reduce manual effort in retail environments.
